09.05.2026.

Training a large model seemingly successfully on three english-croatian datasets.

The current model translates only one way en->hr.

Needs to be evaulated on some actual test sets with standard neural translation benchmarks.
Vibe evaluation show some weakpoints:
- empty sentences churn out bible text (empty strings not in dataset)
- model cannot handle multi-sentence text at all (probably never in dataset)
- model is decent gramatically but lacks vocabulary.
- all caps performance degrades drastically. Model also sensitive to capitalized words (e.g. bible, Bible)

